main event: A witness in Sebeka, Minnesota saw a large, bright object with many colored lights on March 15, 1967.
interesting points: The object had very bright lights on the top and had a slight motion.
The object disappeared in a bright light and continued on.
The witness estimated the speed of the object as 35 mph and the distance as 1 mile away.
The witness's lights on their car went out and on repeatedly while the object was present.
The witness said the object made a whistling sound as it moved over the building and out of sight behind trees.
sighted object: Large, bright object with many colored lights
